cast.name: 托尼·阿姆斯特朗 Tony Armstrong

writer.name: 杰克·雅布斯利 Jack Yabsley

introduction: EVERY DAY IS AN UNDERWATER PRESCHOOL ADVENTURE ON A STUNNING CORAL REEFLed by their gentle turtle teacher Mr. Flip, the little Reefies – Ray, Surg, Ginger, Stripes, Oli, Chips and the Snappers - learn all about life beneath the waves. With stories, songs, excursions and games, every day is as colourful as the coral around them.Narrated by Emma Watkins (The Wiggles), and combining astounding real life underwater footage with charming, funny character voices, Reef School is created and developed by the award-winning ABC Children’s and Family Department.In series two, the Reefies make some new friends, including Shelley the dolphin (voiced by Heartbreak High’s Chloe Hayden) and Mr Bwap the eel (voiced by TikTok creator Luke Springer aka Mr Luke).Children and parents alike will delight in the Reefies’ daily adventures, while being awed by the wondrous underwater setting.
